features.text:
"The Metaverse Is Coming"

This artwork is inspired by Nam June Paik's video art and also an homage to "the more, the better", one of his masterpieces.

Source of Content : ORACLE 2021 - ‘Hymn From Future’ trailer, The Sandbox New Official Teaser 2021, Decentraland Public Launch trailer, Somnium Space Public Launch Trailer, Cryptovoxels Trailer, Wilder World Trailer

collectible.name: The Love Gnomes Lamp
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
Through the winter, 80% of new residents to Scarcity searched for the gnomes and their stories, and the love for the gnomes grew. This lamp is for those who searched.

Happy Valentine's Day 2022!

collectible.author: 0x36354da80c30e3b1045ae2dd7640a99d12d7bcbb
collectible.description: 1 of 5 modular tech artifact wearables discovered on Scarcity CyberPunk timeline. These are designed to fit together in many different ways. Cyborg it up.

collectible.name: The Lost Gnomes Lamp
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
When new Scarcity residents got to the island, they started finding hints of a lost gnome civilization, but no sights of gnomes themselves. What happened to them?

This lamp should aid in looking for discoveries throughout the winter.

1 lamp will be airdropped to each current resident, with a small reserve left for new residents or awards. 7.5% of secondary sales go towards planting trees in the real world! Let's see how many we can plant in the new year.

~ Happy Solstice 2021! ~

collectible.name: Basic Gnome Hat of the Fire Faction
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description: It's raining hats! If you've received this Scarcity airdrop, it means the discovery you presented was linked to a certain gnome faction determined by its color or properties. You can team up with others in your faction to create new lore, improved hats, other faction items, themed art shows, contests, or other events! Extra hats will be available for purchase if you'd like to switch factions or invite a friend to the story who doesn't own land. All proceeds will go to planting real life trees.

collectible.name: Uncommon Barnacled Movathyst in a River Stone
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
This mostly flat river stone is of the lost gnomes Fire faction. Displaying gems in the community was meant to represent the powerful bond between past, present and future generations throughout the ages.

Besides looks, some river stones harnessed magical powers. This Barnacled Movathyst was often used in making clothes, as it was easy to cut seams with it's sharp edges. It was also a good luck charm to increase a shop's sales.

After the limited copies are distributed, the remaining quantity of this NFT *might* be burned.
